        "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified-1\n\nBuild Failed \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/dcaegen2-collectors-hv-ves-master-verify-java/973/ : FAILURE\n\nBuild failed to find artifact org.onap.dcaegen2.services.sdk:hvvesclient-protobuf:jar:1.3.3 needed for sub-project org.onap.dcaegen2.collectors.hv-ves:hv-collector-domain:jar:1.3.0-SNAPSHOT. Check correct groupId, artifactId and version. This may also indicate a problem with nexus. Another possibility is that this is a -SNAPSHOT version and it has expired from nexus -- in that case check with the project which provides the artifact. ( https://jenkins.onap.org/job/dcaegen2-collectors-hv-ves-master-verify-java/973/ )\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/dcaegen2-collectors-hv-ves-master-verify-java/973",
